This is a reference implementation of the AIMEM Bundle Format
specified in draft-vu-aimem-bundle (IETF Independent Submission).

The reference implementation is intentionally minimal — it implements
only the encoding and transport layers defined by the specification.
The reasoning layer (recall ranking, sleep cycles, neural graph
reasoning, etc.) is intentionally NOT included; production implementers
are expected to provide their own reasoning layer behind the same
Bundle interface.

For a production implementation with full reasoning capabilities,
see https://memoryai.dev/.
